property_sql_factory_datasets.sql:
SELECT 
    'ApplyCustomerInvoiceLine' || '::' || "CustomerInvoiceLine"."ID"   AS "ID",
    "PreviousCustomerInvoice"."ID"                                     AS "PreviousCustomerInvoice",
    "CustomerInvoiceLine"."CreationTime"                               AS "Time",
    "CustomerInvoice"."CustomerInvoiceType"                            AS "DocumentCategory",
    'Apply'                                                            AS "Label"
FROM "o_custom_CustomerInvoiceLine" AS "CustomerInvoiceLine"
    LEFT JOIN "o_custom_CustomerInvoice" AS "CustomerInvoice"
        ON "CustomerInvoice"."ID" = "CustomerInvoiceLine"."CustomerInvoice_ID"
    LEFT JOIN "o_custom_CustomerInvoice" AS "PreviousCustomerInvoice"
        ON "PreviousCustomerInvoice"."ID" = "CustomerInvoiceLine"."PreviousCustomerInvoice"
WHERE "CustomerInvoiceLine"."CreationTime" IS NOT NULL
    AND "PreviousCustomerInvoice"."CustomerInvoiceType" = 'CustomerInvoice'
    AND "CustomerInvoice"."CustomerInvoiceType" IN ('CreditMemo', 'DebitMemo')

sql_factory_datasets.sql:
-- Invoice lines
SELECT 
    'ApplyCustomerInvoiceLine' || '::' || "CustomerInvoiceLine"."ID"     AS "ID",
    "PreviousCustomerInvoiceLine"."ID"                                   AS "PreviousCustomerInvoiceLine"
FROM "o_custom_CustomerInvoiceLine" AS "CustomerInvoiceLine"
    LEFT JOIN "o_custom_CustomerInvoice" AS "CustomerInvoice"
        ON "CustomerInvoice"."ID" = "CustomerInvoiceLine"."CustomerInvoice_ID"
    LEFT JOIN "o_custom_CustomerInvoice" AS "PreviousCustomerInvoice"
        ON "PreviousCustomerInvoice"."ID" = "CustomerInvoiceLine"."PreviousCustomerInvoice"
    LEFT JOIN "o_custom_CustomerInvoiceLine" AS "PreviousCustomerInvoiceLine"
        ON "PreviousCustomerInvoiceLine"."CustomerInvoice_ID" = "PreviousCustomerInvoice"."ID"
WHERE "CustomerInvoiceLine"."CreationTime" IS NOT NULL
    AND "PreviousCustomerInvoice"."CustomerInvoiceType" = 'CustomerInvoice'
    AND "CustomerInvoice"."CustomerInvoiceType" IN ('CreditMemo', 'DebitMemo')
